KEY PARTNERS:Key partners enable a business capability that allows your business model to be successful. The business model is leveraging the partner for one of several reasons e.g. technology transfer, scale, resource, channel accessWho are our Key Partners?Which Key Resources are we acquiring from partners?Which Key Activities do partners perform?What Channels do Key Partners enable?Which partners are digitally integrated?
